          <p><strong>Tech stack:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>.NET 8 / ASP\.NET Core Razor Pages</li>
            <li>C# 12, Entity Framework Core (SQL Server)</li>
            <li>Bootstrap 5</li>
            <li>Windows Authentication (Negotiate / NTLM / Kerberos)</li>
            <li>Deployed on IIS (dedicated host)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
